<content-block status="WIP" name="Modal">
  <p slot="description">Add dialogs to your site for lightboxes, user notifications, or completely custom content.</p>

  <content-example>
    <div slot="demo">
      <div id="Modal-1" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" class="modal is-active is-static">
        <div class="modal__card">
          <div class="modal__header">
            <h5 class="modal__title">Modal title</h5>
            <button class="modal__close button" js-modal="closeModal">
              {% render 'icon-misc' with icon: 'close' %}
            </button>
          </div>

          <div class="modal__body">
            <h1>Hello World</h1>

            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla accumsan, metus ultrices eleifend gravida, nulla nunc varius lectus, nec rutrum justo nibh eu lectus. Ut vulputate semper dui. Fusce erat odio, sollicitudin vel erat vel, interdum mattis neque.</p>

